<h4><a href="https://9to5mac.com/2020/09/29/iphone-12-production-at-full-tilt/">为生产 iPhone 12，富士康国庆也没假放了</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369766" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone-12-production-at-full-tilt.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="750" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone-12-production-at-full-tilt.jpg 1500w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone-12-production-at-full-tilt-360x180.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone-12-production-at-full-tilt-768x384.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone-12-production-at-full-tilt-1024x512.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /></p>
<p>9to5mac 消息，富士康为了生产 iPhone 12，已经开启夜班，进入 24 小时生产模式，报道称员工在国庆和中秋假期也将继续加班。</p>
<p>富士康员工表示，iPhone 生产线向从 9 月 18 日后开始加入，至少留在岗位 90 天，工作至少 55 天的员工提供一万元的奖金。</p>
